pylapp.tapster.client.android.assistants

Interface UiNotifierStub

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    UiNotifierSkeleton

    public UiNotifierStub

    Stub based on design pattern Bridge which provides the declarations of methods to call so as to deal with an object which can make notifications to the user interface. This pattern is used so as to avoid the assistant to have too many dependencies and code about the UI.
